-- Chrysler says wants federal bridge loan to preserve company
-- 
-- Tue Dec 2, 2008 10:42am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/12/02/us-autos-bailout-chrysler-idUSTRE4B15A920081202

 

 BALTIMORE  (Reuters) - Chrysler President Jim Press told Port of Baltimore workers on Tuesday that Chrysler is only asking Congress for bridge loan to preserve company. 

 Highlights: * Says Chrysler has a plan to compete and make tough choices for future. * Says Chrysler is already seeing progress in quality, warranty claims down 29 percent.